that I brought this up.

285
00:30:48,079 --> 00:30:51,289
This is why you should
always be straightforward, right?

286
00:30:52,720 --> 00:30:55,789
- Exactly.
- I'm so relieved.

287
00:31:10,769 --> 00:31:13,880
He was so frustrated...

288
00:31:13,980 --> 00:31:15,710
when Ro Woon ignored his feelings.

289
00:31:19,619 --> 00:31:20,950
What about my feelings?

290
00:31:52,819 --> 00:31:53,920
Gyo Ri.

291
00:31:54,650 --> 00:31:56,690
- Yes?
- Well...

292
00:31:57,650 --> 00:32:01,289
Would you like to take charge of
the jewelry brand project?

293
00:32:01,319 --> 00:32:03,160
What? Me?

294
00:32:03,190 --> 00:32:04,259
Yes.

295
00:32:06,059 --> 00:32:07,430
With Se Jong.

296
00:32:08,869 --> 00:32:09,930
Me?

297
00:32:12,170 --> 00:32:15,039
What exactly are the two of us
supposed to do?

298
00:32:15,140 --> 00:32:17,440
Yoo Hee, Sun Bong,
please help them.

299
00:32:18,009 --> 00:32:20,109
- Okay.
- Okay.

300
00:32:27,180 --> 00:32:28,319
What was that?

301
00:32:28,849 --> 00:32:30,250
Are you playing Cupid?

302
00:32:32,990 --> 00:32:35,589
I just thought the two of them
could achieve synergy.

303
00:32:44,630 --> 00:32:47,269
This and... This one is pretty.

304
00:32:47,970 --> 00:32:49,069
What do you think?

305
00:32:50,109 --> 00:32:51,609
Was it Ms. Chae?

306
00:33:01,380 --> 00:33:04,349
Hello. You must be here to see Boss.

307
00:33:04,619 --> 00:33:06,059
He just went that way.

308
00:33:06,089 --> 00:33:08,160
No. I'm here to see Woo Il.

309
00:33:08,890 --> 00:33:10,589
I need to measure his finger
for our wedding rings.

310
00:33:14,960 --> 00:33:16,970
If you have time,

311
00:33:17,730 --> 00:33:19,470
