Ideas don't come from
analyzing data.

316
00:33:41,119 --> 00:33:42,730
Creativity comes from insight.

317
00:33:42,829 --> 00:33:45,400
It's supposed to pop out
all of a sudden.

318
00:33:46,630 --> 00:33:50,069
When will it finally pop out?

319
00:33:51,630 --> 00:33:55,539
Stuck in the office,
my brain is working so slowly.

320
00:33:57,970 --> 00:33:59,480
Hey, wait.

321
00:34:05,920 --> 00:34:07,579
Why did Boss,

322
