Se Jong, you really don't look like
a chairman's grandson.

367
00:36:29,030 --> 00:36:30,690
Do you mean I look poor?

368
00:36:30,730 --> 00:36:32,929
- That's not what I mean.
- To tell you the truth,

369
00:36:34,130 --> 00:36:35,329
I get that a lot.

370
00:36:37,130 --> 00:36:39,199
By the way, it's true.

371
00:36:40,039 --> 00:36:41,739
What? You're mean.

372
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:44,670
- You pay for the food.
- What?

373
00:36:45,510 --> 00:36:47,309
This doesn't even cost that much.

374
00:36:51,510 --> 00:36:53,679
I finally have an idea.

375
00:36:54,019 --> 00:36:56,489
Collaboration with an artist.

376
00:36:58,989 --> 00:37:00,090
Gosh.

377
00:37:00,190 --> 00:37:02,730
You mentioned intuitions
and getting inspirations.

378
00:37:02,760 --> 00:37:04,929
This is what you came up with?
A collaboration?

379
00:37:04,960 --> 00:37:06,699
Hear me out.

380
00:37:07,300 --> 00:37:09,630
A jewelry brand with history
and traditions...

381
00:37:09,670 --> 00:37:12,000
along with the taste of a young
and rising artist...

382
00:37:12,030 --> 00:37:14,199
will result in an innovative design.

383
00:37:14,300 --> 00:37:16,469
We'll make them limited editions
to make it more valuable.

384
00:37:17,039 --> 00:37:21,840
I'm not sure. It won't be easy
working with artists.

385
00:37:22,139 --> 00:37:25,849
Boss.
I mean, Hwan Gi, what do you think?

386
00:37:28,679 --> 00:37:30,050
What about you, Gyo Ri?

387
00:37:30,250 --> 00:37:32,190
Pardon? Me?

388
00:37:34,090 --> 00:37:39,030
I think Se Jong's idea is great.

389
00:37:39,130 --> 00:37:41,199
I'll support him.

390
00:37:45,199 --> 00:37:46,469
Come up with a proposal.

391
00:37:47,070 --> 00:37:49,309
I got it. Gyo Ri.

392
00:37:52,210 --> 00:37:53,280
Great.

393
00:37:54,409 --> 00:37:57,280
- It's going to be hard work.
- Exactly.

394
00:38:05,250 --> 00:38:08,320
