395
00:38:22,099 --> 00:38:23,610
You seem fine.

396
00:38:46,860 --> 00:38:47,860
My flowers.

397
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:56,110
My pictures.

398
00:39:04,210 --> 00:39:06,280
Mom and Ji Hye's pictures...

399
00:39:20,659 --> 00:39:23,500
Where are Mom and Ji Hye's pictures?

400
00:39:24,329 --> 00:39:25,530
Don't look for them.

401
00:39:26,269 --> 00:39:28,840
You should forget about everything.

402
00:39:33,110 --> 00:39:36,280
I lived the way you wanted
until now.

403
00:39:37,210 --> 00:39:40,420
I was dead quiet
whenever I came home.

404
00:39:44,019 --> 00:39:45,250
I can't do it anymore.

405
00:39:47,059 --> 00:39:48,860
I have to be by his side.

406
00:39:58,000 --> 00:40:00,369
He's going to come soon.

407
00:40:00,940 --> 00:40:03,409
There will be a moment of truth.

408
00:40:04,369 --> 00:40:05,409
Chae Ro Woon.

409
00:40:05,909 --> 00:40:08,110
You should know
since you've seen him.

410
00:40:08,309 --> 00:40:10,150
He's not a bad person.

411
00:40:27,599 --> 00:40:28,829
I'm going for a smoke.

412
00:40:56,789 --> 00:40:59,030
Is she here again?

413
00:42:07,760 --> 00:42:09,059
Here.

414
00:42:10,199 --> 00:42:11,670
Have you calmed down?

415
00:42:17,469 --> 00:42:18,510
Then...

416
00:42:19,840 --> 00:42:23,480
you should go back home.

417
00:42:28,019 --> 00:42:30,590
Crying won't help. You have to go.

418
00:42:32,920 --> 00:42:34,519
You're so evil.

419
00:42:38,960 --> 00:42:39,960
Hwan Gi.

420
00:42:42,260 --> 00:42:44,599
Ro Woon, you're here too?

421
00:42:45,769 --> 00:42:46,969
I thought you were alone.

422
00:42:49,139 --> 00:42:52,780
Is this why you were trying
to send me home?

423
00:42:54,780 --> 00:42:55,980
Yun Jung.

424
00:42:56,780 --> 00:42:58,780
You didn't tell me you were coming.

425
00:43:00,579 --> 00:43:02,519
I had no idea you were with
another woman,

426
00:43:03,190 --> 00:43:05,250
let alone making her cry.

427
00:43:06,190 --> 00:43:08,190
What's going on anyway?

428
00:43:09,690 --> 00:43:11,590
Are you being dumped?

429
00:43:11,889 --> 00:43:13,400
If so, I'll step out for a minute.

430
00:43:15,860 --> 00:43:17,769
I didn't make her cry. No.

431
00:43:19,199 --> 00:43:21,570
I see. You're not being dumped.

432
00:43:23,070 --> 00:43:24,710
Should the three of us drink, then?

433
00:43:24,840 --> 00:43:27,010
- Three?
- No?

434
00:43:27,940 --> 00:43:30,079
Ro Woon has to go. It's late.

435
00:43:30,550 --> 00:43:33,480
Is that so? I'd appreciate that.

436
00:43:34,349 --> 00:43:37,289
