together.

437
00:43:37,949 --> 00:43:40,719
- Fine. Shall we go over there?
- Sure.

438
00:43:46,429 --> 00:43:47,429
Goodness.

439
00:43:49,630 --> 00:43:53,369
We'll have one quick drink
and go on our ways.

440
00:43:53,769 --> 00:43:55,599
Okay? All right?

441
00:44:11,019 --> 00:44:13,920
Hwan Gi sat beside me, Ro Woon.

442
00:44:15,519 --> 00:44:16,989
What are you saying?

443
00:44:20,730 --> 00:44:22,300
Let's drink wine.

444
00:44:29,269 --> 00:44:30,340
I'll do it.

445
00:44:30,769 --> 00:44:33,039
I'll do it, give it to me. Come on.

446
00:44:37,280 --> 00:44:38,750
Isn't he so sweet?

447
00:44:40,980 --> 00:44:44,320
He's thoughtful and polite.
On top of that, he's handsome.

448
00:44:44,789 --> 00:44:46,059
He's quite athletic too.

449
00:44:46,360 --> 00:44:48,460
Don't make me feel uncomfortable.

450
00:44:49,559 --> 00:44:51,730
He doesn't talk much,

451
00:44:52,590 --> 00:44:54,960
but I find that sexy.

452
00:44:56,070 --> 00:44:59,030
Sexy? Hey, stop it.

453
00:45:02,440 --> 00:45:04,869
She and I are going to fight
over you.

454
00:45:05,170 --> 00:45:06,409
It's been officially announced.

455
00:45:06,440 --> 00:45:08,579
Stop joking around.

456
00:45:09,079 --> 00:45:10,579
I mean it.

457
00:45:11,750 --> 00:45:14,780
Ro Woon. Don't you admit
that the two of us...

458
00:45:14,880 --> 00:45:16,889
look better together?

459
00:45:17,019 --> 00:45:19,820
- Gosh.
- Seriously.

460
00:45:20,360 --> 00:45:24,090
Only if I was a little bit taller,
I wouldn't be inferior.

461
00:45:30,829 --> 00:45:32,369
His first love.

462
00:45:33,070 --> 00:45:34,170
Is that you?

463
00:45:37,309 --> 00:45:38,539
You are.

464
00:45:38,570 --> 00:45:41,679
So you're the one that made him
hide behind his black hoodie.

465
00:45:41,780 --> 00:45:43,449
I see.

466
00:45:44,050 --> 00:45:46,380
- Are you talking about university?
- Don't talk about it.

467
00:45:49,019 --> 00:45:50,119
