474
00:46:07,369 --> 00:46:09,539
By the way, when did you...

475
00:46:09,869 --> 00:46:12,940
start preferring little kids?

476
00:46:15,440 --> 00:46:16,480
It's...

477
00:46:18,550 --> 00:46:19,820
Kids?

478
00:46:22,650 --> 00:46:26,190
