479
00:46:27,789 --> 00:46:29,630
I wasn't going to say this,

480
00:46:30,690 --> 00:46:34,400
but we even slept together
for two days in a row.

481
00:46:37,900 --> 00:46:39,199
- You probably just slept.
- Yes.

482
00:46:41,400 --> 00:46:42,469
