asked to kiss one of us now?

491
00:47:12,329 --> 00:47:13,639
I can't believe you.

492
00:47:14,500 --> 00:47:15,739
Gosh, seriously.

493
00:47:16,000 --> 00:47:18,110
- Yes. Tell us, Boss.
- Tell us.

494
00:47:18,510 --> 00:47:20,210
What is the matter
with the two of you today?

495
00:47:21,110 --> 00:47:22,840
- Tell us.
- Tell you what?

496
00:47:24,380 --> 00:47:25,710
Tell us, please.

497
00:47:32,150 --> 00:47:33,260
A kiss?

498
00:47:40,559 --> 00:47:44,230
