- I drank too much.

499
00:47:44,269 --> 00:47:45,429
- Yun Jung.
- Hey.

500
00:47:45,469 --> 00:47:47,440
- Ro Woon.
- Yes?

501
00:47:47,840 --> 00:47:50,639
- You two should kiss each other.
- Ro Woon, are you all right?

502
00:47:50,739 --> 00:47:54,010
Come on. Gosh, Yun Jung...

503
00:47:54,039 --> 00:47:58,949
Gosh, Yun Jung... That time...

504
00:48:00,119 --> 00:48:02,650
- Ro Woon.
- I feel like I'm having a deja vu.

505
00:48:03,250 --> 00:48:05,820
- Ro Woon, Ro Woon.
- Ro Woon?

506
00:48:05,849 --> 00:48:07,190
Why did you say
you didn't want to go?

507
00:48:08,320 --> 00:48:10,130
I'm over here.

508
00:48:14,900 --> 00:48:17,099
- What? What now?
- That day... Water...

509
00:48:18,099 --> 00:48:20,739
- Then this... My gosh.
- Gosh, you're making me blush.

510
00:48:20,769 --> 00:48:22,900
