511
00:48:23,110 --> 00:48:25,639
- It's a secret.
- It's just our secret.

512
00:48:25,670 --> 00:48:27,079
I can't tell you.

513
00:48:27,110 --> 00:48:30,309
Anyway, you two should do it.
Kiss each other. Come on.

514
00:48:30,409 --> 00:48:31,679
- What's this guy saying?
- Goodness.

515
00:48:31,710 --> 00:48:33,349
Let me do a little inspection
before you kiss.

516
00:48:33,679 --> 00:48:36,949
