517
00:48:36,989 --> 00:48:38,849
- Don't do that.
- Show me your teeth.

518
00:48:38,889 --> 00:48:40,619
- Cut me some slack.
- What's this about?

519
00:48:40,659 --> 00:48:43,760
- Yun Jung, let me see your teeth.
- I check my teeth often now.

520
00:48:43,789 --> 00:48:45,730
- Show me your teeth.
- Stop it already.

521
00:48:52,530 --> 00:48:54,969
You can have him.
I don't think I want him.

522
00:48:55,969 --> 00:48:58,340
Then shall we go finish our drinks?

523
00:48:59,780 --> 00:49:00,840
Sounds good.

524
00:49:08,320 --> 00:49:11,989
Yun Jung, how much do you know?

525
00:49:14,119 --> 00:49:15,559
I don't know everything either.

526
00:49:15,820 --> 00:49:17,360
I just know a bit about you.

527
00:49:20,900 --> 00:49:23,030
When will I find out everything?

528
00:49:23,199 --> 00:49:25,599
Just trust Hwan Gi
and give him some more time.

529
00:49:25,630 --> 00:49:27,099
Don't be so impatient.

